c=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349030/extras/98bb040bdf668c3a42f96785e0b88b7d.webm?t=1741788766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349030/extras/98bb040bdf668c3a42f96785e0b88b7d.mp4?t=1741788766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Endless magic: with 2 different possible endings, 14 characters epilogues to explore and many CGs to unlock, the replayability is high",
